{# Template pour Strategy Builder — Proposition de logique de stratégie #}
{# Utilisé par agents/strategy_builder.py pour générer une proposition JSON #}

Design a trading strategy proposal for the following objective.

## OBJECTIVE
{{ objective }}

## AVAILABLE INDICATORS (use ONLY these)
{% for ind in available_indicators %}
- {{ ind }}
{% endfor %}

## ITERATION {{ iteration }} / {{ max_iterations }}

{% if last_metrics -%}
## LAST BACKTEST RESULTS
- Sharpe Ratio: {{ last_metrics.sharpe_ratio|format_float(3) }}
- Total Return: {{ last_metrics.total_return_pct|format_float(2) }}%
- Max Drawdown: {{ last_metrics.max_drawdown_pct|format_float(2) }}%
- Win Rate: {{ last_metrics.win_rate_pct|format_float(1) }}%
- Trades: {{ last_metrics.total_trades }}
- Profit Factor: {{ last_metrics.profit_factor|format_float(2) }}

Best Sharpe so far: {{ best_sharpe|format_float(3) }}

{% endif -%}

{% if last_analysis -%}
## LAST ANALYSIS
{{ last_analysis }}

{% endif -%}

{% if last_code -%}
## CURRENT CODE (to iterate on)
```python
{{ last_code }}
```

{% endif -%}

{% if iteration_history and iteration_history|length > 0 -%}
## ITERATION HISTORY
{% for h in iteration_history %}
- Iter {{ h.iteration }}: hypothesis="{{ h.hypothesis }}" | sharpe={{ h.sharpe|default("N/A") }} | error={{ h.error|default("none") }}
{% endfor %}

{% endif -%}

## INSTRUCTIONS
{% if last_code -%}
Based on the previous results, propose MODIFICATIONS to the current strategy logic.
Focus on:
- Improving signal quality (fewer false signals)
- Better risk management (stop-loss, take-profit)
- Adding/removing indicator conditions
- Adjusting entry/exit thresholds
{% else -%}
Propose a NEW strategy from scratch.
Choose indicators that match the objective.
Design clear entry/exit rules and risk management.
{% endif %}

Respond with a JSON object containing:
{
  "strategy_name": "descriptive_name",
  "hypothesis": "what you expect this change to achieve",
  "used_indicators": ["indicator1", "indicator2"],
  "indicator_params": {"indicator1": {"period": 14}},
  "entry_long_logic": "conditions for entering LONG",
  "entry_short_logic": "conditions for entering SHORT",
  "exit_logic": "conditions for exiting positions",
  "risk_management": "stop-loss and take-profit rules",
  "default_params": {"param1": value},
  "parameter_specs": {"param1": {"min": 5, "max": 50, "default": 14, "type": "int"}}
}
